The paper proposes a novel coordination module for multi-agent reinforcement learning (MARL) in team competition games. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which is the primary focus of the paper. The paper also deals with multi-agent systems and game theory, which suggests that it could belong to cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) and cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory). Additionally, the paper proposes a new approach to MARL, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
